{"tid":247983,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[金庸JJ] 認真問：究竟小說版定電視劇","createTime":"2017-05-18T08:15:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-22T11:44:00.000Z","uid":111512,"like":3,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3caad72995fdd6ef9afe502e83c6c540466e803b","tid":247983,"uid":111512,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T08:15:02.000Z","msg":"小弟係金庸愛好者<br />\n見到近日好多post講關於金庸都係新版射丁劇有關<br />\n好奇一問<br />\n<br />\n究竟小說定電視劇？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：識睇一定睇電視劇，有畫面感<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：無睇過小說版咪同人講睇過金庸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可以既話講埋原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申睇大部分既金庸作品都係電視劇版本（包括新舊鹿鼎記，新舊射丁，新舊神丁，碧血例等等）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最近sem break打算由小說版碧血劍開始睇起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c11a2d290970c213873a160b921aeadc7f652674","tid":247983,"uid":71712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T08:16:31.000Z","msg":"碧血好睇<br />\n夏青青我至愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"668dade985936a31ff0e6c50610b726d77e945a4","tid":247983,"uid":111512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T08:18:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>碧血好睇<br />\n夏青青我至愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇小說版定電視劇？<br />\n<br />\n我就睇過電視劇<br />\n睇緊小說版<br />\n<br />\n夏青青<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28fbb99ec5bed77075c5059828533641e8656694","tid":247983,"uid":111512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T08:29:28.000Z","msg":"金庸post無人回<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實係咪開錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\